## Rules

- **Never capture login screens with real credentials** — use seed user only
- **Always use seed data** — no empty states unless documenting the empty state specifically
- **Consistent seed data** across web and mobile captures
- **Include status bar on mobile** — confirms the platform to the reader
- **Exclude browser chrome on web** — app content only
- **Capture light mode by default** — capture dark mode separately if supported
- **Descriptive filenames** — `invoices-list-filtered.png` not `screenshot-1.png`
- **Don't annotate** — clean screenshots only. Annotations are a separate design task.
- **If a capture fails, don't block** — log it, move on, report at the end
